<taxonomicName id="4C78F1F8E802513E7FF5FC3B3D3EFBE1" authorityName="Yin &amp; Li" authorityYear="2013" box="[419,639,1007,1030]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Labomimus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bannaus">
<emphasis id="B90C5669E802513E7FF5FC3B3D3EFBE1" box="[419,639,1007,1030]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Labomimus bannaus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
can be readily recognized by a large disc-like process at the apex of antennomere 9, basally expanded antennomere 10, curved antennomere 11, as well as by the unique form of aedeagus. This species was originally described from Xishuangbanna, 
<collectingRegion id="49BC4499E802513E7EC1FB5B3FAAFB41" box="[151,235,1167,1190]" country="China" name="Yunnan" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Yunnan</collectingRegion>
, southern 
<collectingCountry id="F36FCAEBE802513E7F01FB5B3ED8FB41" box="[343,409,1167,1190]" name="China" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">China</collectingCountry>
, and is here newly recorded from 
<collectingCountry id="F36FCAEBE802513E7EC1FB7B3FB3FB21" box="[151,242,1199,1222]" name="Vietnam" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="F36FCAEBE802513E7F7BFB7B3E24FB21" box="[301,357,1199,1222]" name="Laos" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Laos</collectingCountry>
. There is no obvious morphological difference between the population from 
<collectingCountry id="F36FCAEBE802513E7C1FFB1B3DC8FB01" box="[585,649,1231,1254]" name="China" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">China</collectingCountry>
and those from 
<collectingCountry id="F36FCAEBE802513E7E84FB3B3E47FAE1" box="[210,262,1263,1286]" name="Laos" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Laos</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="F36FCAEBE802513E7F6FFB3B3ED6FAE1" box="[313,407,1263,1286]" name="Vietnam" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C362D9F0E802513E7EC1FADB3ED7FA61" pageId="2" pageNumber="37" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8BC78A7BE802513E7EC1FADB3ED7FA61" blockId="2.[151,761,1007,1414]" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis id="B90C5669E802513E7EC1FADB3E6BFAC1" bold="true" box="[151,298,1295,1318]" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Distribution.</emphasis>
China: Yunnan; Vietnam: Ninh Bình, Đồng Nai; Laos: 
<collectingRegion id="49BC4499E802513E7F58FAFB3ED9FAA1" box="[270,408,1327,1350]" country="Laos" name="Bolikhamxai" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Bolikhamsai</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49BC4499E802513E7FF4FAFB3D6EFAA1" box="[418,559,1327,1350]" country="Laos" name="Khammouan" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Ehammouan</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49BC4499E802513E7C6FFAFB3DF9FAA1" box="[569,696,1327,1350]" country="Laos" name="Champasak" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Champasak</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49BC4499E802513E7C97FAFB3FFCFA81" country="Laos" name="Attapu" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Attapeu</collectingRegion>
(Y I N et al. 2013a; this paper). 
<emphasis id="B90C5669E802513E7C53FA9B3ED7FA61" bold="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">
First country records for 
<collectingCountry id="F36FCAEBE802513E7EE9FABB3FB7FA61" box="[191,246,1391,1414]" name="Laos" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Laos</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="F36FCAEBE802513E7F78FABB3ED0FA61" box="[302,401,1391,1414]" name="Vietnam" pageId="2" pageNumber="37">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
